{"id": 2323, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都观察到过哪些自我催眠式社交行为？", "description": "“TA一定是太忙了才不回我消息，嗯。”（题图来自：iStock © juanmagarcia）", "record_count": 3158, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180504190306Z65VojztXhEDygIS.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-05-16T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 282377, "content": "他肯定生气了，都不回我，怎么办怎么办", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1347874}, {"id": 282378, "content": "照片永远发背影 大家都会觉得小姐姐应该是美翻了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 934917}, {"id": 282381, "content": "试过wx和手机失联三天，结果开机以后很多未接电话，很多wx信息", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1347978}, {"id": 282644, "content": "额，好喜欢逛好奇心??大家个个都是人才，说话又好听", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1322326}, {"id": 289046, "content": "通常不想回装死，我一定是睡着了/有事了/手机没电了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1383050}, {"id": 282656, "content": "应该是有事等会儿就会回信息了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 818716}, {"id": 282150, "content": "我这么loser是世界的错", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 532900}, {"id": 282406, "content": "走进电梯感觉所有人都在看我！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 782034}, {"id": 282151, "content": "一定是对方手机掉厕所了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346258}, {"id": 282152, "content": "说到一半，他（她）怎么不回了？估计是在街上或者在忙吧？", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1326711}, {"id": 282153, "content": "不努力不是我懒，而是因为我不愿意", "image": null, "praise_count": 240, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346274}, {"id": 282154, "content": "……", "image": "img/option/option/201805161118385fZOw6TFbH9Wpnhr", "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1339680}, {"id": 282155, "content": "他一定是不好意思才没找我", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1345112}, {"id": 282157, "content": "有刚认识异性连续几天和你联系总会以为是对你有意思", "image": "img/option/option/20180516112517UGlHibFJOW2SsX18", "praise_count": 73, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303339}, {"id": 282925, "content": "朋友圈设置为三天可见，新加的人认为我是个有故事的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1332428}, {"id": 282158, "content": "说喜欢我的人 渐渐的降低了联系我的频率，我就开始不回信息了，慢慢的我就当他嗝屁了??????", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 380685}, {"id": 282161, "content": "他一定是和我聊天太认真，结果走路时不小心摔了一跤，手机掉进了下水道，捡起来的时候屏幕碎了触摸无法使用，着急的想回我信息，都快哭了出来却没有一点办法。\n我的嘴角露出一丝微笑:）", "image": null, "praise_count": 141, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1179165}, {"id": 282162, "content": "秒回我，嗯，他肯定喜欢我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 77, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1070047}, {"id": 282163, "content": "朋友圈设置成三天可见，给新加的好友一种本人很高冷的错觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333758}, {"id": 282166, "content": "每次发生点什么举国皆知的舆论事件，比如某明星出轨，某名人爱不爱国等，总要发点什么“正确的观点”来表明自己的政治正确，以彰显自己的主流价值观，来完成主流站队而显得自己不那么孤立。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088658}, {"id": 282167, "content": "游戏玩的菜：什么蠢队友\n游戏玩的好：都是我厉害", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897440}, {"id": 282168, "content": "这么好的女孩，我肯定追不到……", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 103310}, {"id": 282169, "content": "他一定是去世了才不再找我", "image": null, "praise_count": 99, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 523416}, {"id": 282170, "content": "自己说完自己要说的后 为了自己不等对方的消息就说再见……", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1344509}, {"id": 282938, "content": "11111", "image": "img/option/option/20180521140317fMSuoT2QsOWYRkHd.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224458}, {"id": 282173, "content": "看完消息，心里已经回复过了", "image": null, "praise_count": 441, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1344988}, {"id": 282174, "content": "她对我有意思", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340949}, {"id": 282177, "content": "脑补～～～", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205377}, {"id": 282179, "content": "喜欢的男孩子不喜欢我。他未来的女朋友一定长得比我丑比我矮比我没钱比我笨。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1344725}, {"id": 282180, "content": "一定是ta喜欢我才会回我", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1323930}, {"id": 282436, "content": "得到的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1348219}, {"id": 282181, "content": "全世界都在跟我作对_(:з」∠)_诸如此类", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106176}, {"id": 282437, "content": "把自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1348219}, {"id": 282182, "content": "它真的洗澡去了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337538}, {"id": 282184, "content": "Shitting some ‘smartass’ comments here and be like duhh lol", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346386}, {"id": 283208, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈，我被你们笑死了，怎么你们自我催眠那么厉害", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693756}, {"id": 282185, "content": "朋友圈回复必互动", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271976}, {"id": 282186, "content": "就是懒，就是low，就是懦弱", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1345916}, {"id": 282187, "content": "他可能在默默关注我", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346410}, {"id": 282189, "content": "比如可能要遇到那种关系尴尬的人 心里想着：我看见他我会尴尬 他看见我他也会尴尬 那既然他也会尴尬 那我干嘛要尴尬 我大气自然一点让他更尴尬 气死他吧?", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346415}, {"id": 282190, "content": "别人给我点赞就是有意思", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 631496}, {"id": 282191, "content": "她和别人换一个情头肯定不是真心的，只是打赌输了，或者只是为了刺激我。嗯，一定是这样！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1344605}, {"id": 282192, "content": "我做的一切都是应该可以正确没有问题的", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1339791}, {"id": 282194, "content": "问题不大", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1342542}, {"id": 282196, "content": "你对我态度冷，一定是我讨好你不够努力", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297014}, {"id": 282199, "content": "不喜欢我的他一定有难言之隐，比如他其实喜欢的是男孩", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346475}, {"id": 282201, "content": "发完消息后 把会话框删掉 \n让自己忘记发了消息", "image": null, "praise_count": 67, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137519}, {"id": 282202, "content": "嗯，就当是在给死人烧纸吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340063}, {"id": 282206, "content": "默默安慰自己没关系，然后打开日程薄，记录下将在哪一天用完ta后，直接删除好友", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 806190}, {"id": 282207, "content": "表演节目总让我上台，一定是期待我的表现吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346198}]}